{"title":"MAKEUP","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"madara-plum-plum-lip-balm-15ml","title":"MÁDARA Plum Plum Lip Balm 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eIntense hydration and heavenly softness from the very first application. Use alone for a sheer finish or as a base for your favorite lipstick. Lips stay soft, protected and hydrated to perfection. Formulated with deeply moisturising jojoba oil, shea butter and plum oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean, dry lips. Reapply whenever necessary. Use alone for a sheer finish or as a base for your favourite lipstick.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Sorbitan olivate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed Oil, Aroma, Tocopherol, Calendula Officinalis (Calendula) Flower Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Camomile) Flower Extract, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Extract, Propolis Extract, Stevia Rebaudiana Extract, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887773229383,"sku":null,"price":10.4,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-plum-plum-lip-balm-15ml-844261.jpg?v=1739897244"},{"product_id":"magrada-blueberry-tinted-lip-balm-10ml","title":"Magrada Blueberry Tinted Lip Balm 10ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis balm's delightful lightweight formula melts seamlessly into your lips, leaving behind a gorgeous blueberry hue and a radiant, natural shine. Embrace beauty while making a conscious choice—crafted from 100% vegan ingredients and wrapped in eco-friendly packaging, this balm is truly a beauty essential.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean lips as desired. Perfect for use as a nourishing lip balm before applying lipstick or as a glossy finish over lip balm or lip liner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHydroxystearic\/Linolenic\/OleicPolyglycerides, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Candelilla Cera, Aroma (Flavor), CI 77019\/Mica, Dipalmitoyl Hydroxyproline, CI77163\/Bismuth Oxychloride, CI 77491\/Iron Oxide, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Stevia Rebaudiana (Sweetleaf) Extract\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| EU allergen-free\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003ewith a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50848777699655,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-blueberry-tinted-lip-balm-10ml-587083.png?v=1739897252"},{"product_id":"magrada-peach-plump-lip-balm-10ml","title":"Magrada Peach Plump Lip Balm 10ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIndulge your lips with this luscious lip balm, enriched with botanical oils for that perfect shine. If you crave maximum hydration and irresistibly soft, plump lips, this balm is just for you! Immerse yourself in the delightful notes of fresh peach, perfectly blended with nourishing candelilla wax, olive oil, castor oil, and vitamin E. Unique formula not only restores your lips’ natural softness but also locks in moisture for a fuller, more vibrant look. Plus, you can feel good about your choice—our fully recyclable packaging keeps your beauty routine eco-friendly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean lips as desired. Perfect for use as a nourishing lip balm before applying lipstick or as a glossy finish over lip balm or lip liner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHydroxystearic\/Linolenic\/OleicPolyglycerides, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Candelilla Cera, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Dipalmitoyl Hydroxyproline, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Linalool, Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003ewith a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50848815579463,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-peach-plump-lip-balm-10ml-427278.png?v=1739897251"},{"product_id":"hej-organic-peptide-lip-treatment-8ml","title":"HEJ Organic Peptide Lip Treatment 8ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePeptides moisturize your lips, make them shiny and make them look fuller. Castor oil and shea butter make the glazed look perfect. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGlossy finish with care effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePeptides ensure plump lips with a smoothing effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMoisturizing thanks to rinizus oil and shea butter\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCan also be used as an overnight treatment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% fragrance-free \u0026amp; vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply evenly to your lips. As an overnight treatment, you can leave a larger amount on overnight.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis Seed Oil*, Hydroxystearic\/Linolenic\/Oleic Polyglycerides, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate, Euphorbia Cerifera Cera, Pentaerythrityl Tetraisostearate, Palmitoyl Hexapeptide-12, Raphanus Sativus Root Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Stearalkonium Hectorite, Propylene Carbonate, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905836093767,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-peptide-lip-treatment-8ml-265182.png?v=1739897182"},{"product_id":"madara-the-eye-pencil-black","title":"MÁDARA The Eye Pencil Black 1g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFormulated with rich mineral pigments, this natural certified eye pencil delivers vibrant colour and a smooth application to help you create any eye makeup look you desire. Its long-lasting, creamy formula glides onto the skin effortlessly without tugging or pulling, making it ideal for creating smudged smoky eyes or defining the eye shape. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy you'll love it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLong-lasting formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e0% synthetic colourants\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologically and ophthalmologically tested\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFragrance allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Eye Pencil features a wooden barrel and a recyclable plastic cap while the box is made from sustainably sourced paper.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply it directly to the waterline for a more dramatic look. To open and elongate the eyes, draw it close to the lash line. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); C10-18 TRIGLYCERIDES; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*; COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA*; EUPHORBIA CERIFERA CERA; HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL; MICA (CI 77019); TOCOPHEROL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL; ASCORBYL PALMITATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e16% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52308696105287,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-the-eye-pencil-black-1g-5135248.jpg?v=1762389188"},{"product_id":"madara-the-eye-pencil-brown-1g","title":"MÁDARA The Eye Pencil Brown 1g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFormulated with rich mineral pigments, this natural certified eye pencil delivers vibrant colour and a smooth application to help you create any eye makeup look you desire. Its long-lasting, creamy formula glides onto the skin effortlessly without tugging or pulling, making it ideal for creating smudged smoky eyes or defining the eye shape. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy you'll love it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLong-lasting formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e0% synthetic colourants\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologically and ophthalmologically tested\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFragrance allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Eye Pencil features a wooden barrel and a recyclable plastic cap while the box is made from sustainably sourced paper.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply it directly to the waterline for a more dramatic look. To open and elongate the eyes, draw it close to the lash line. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; C10-18 TRIGLYCERIDES; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*; COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA*; HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL; CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); EUPHORBIA CERIFERA CERA*; MICA (CI 77019); CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES); TOCOPHEROL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL; ASCORBYL PALMITATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e15% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52308713144647,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-the-eye-pencil-brown-1g-1075281.jpg?v=1762389183"},{"product_id":"madara-the-brow-pencil-light-brown-1g","title":"MÁDARA The Brow Pencil Light Brown 1g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis creamy eyebrow pencil glides onto the skin smoothly, shaping your brows for a defined and polished look. Formulated with mineral pigments, providing long-lasting shades that blend seamlessly with the colour of your natural brow hairs. Ideal for drawing precise, hair-like strokes or for completely filling in your brows. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy you'll love it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLong-lasting formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e0% synthetic colourants\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologically and ophthalmologically tested\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFragrance allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Brow Pencil features a wooden barrel and recyclable plastic caps while the box is made from sustainably sourced paper.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eComb and shape your eyebrows with the built-in spoolie, following their natural curve. Create a natural brow look by drawing soft, hair-like strokes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e C10-18 TRIGLYCERIDES; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA*; EUPHORBIA CERIFERA CERA; HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) **; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*; MICA (CI 77019)**; CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)**; TOCOPHEROL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL; ASCORBYL PALMITATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e18% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52308719108423,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-the-brow-pencil-light-brown-1g-1591030.jpg?v=1762389185"},{"product_id":"madara-the-brow-pencil-medium-brown-1g","title":"MÁDARA The Brow Pencil Medium Brown 1g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis creamy eyebrow pencil glides onto the skin smoothly, shaping your brows for a defined and polished look. Formulated with mineral pigments, providing long-lasting shades that blend seamlessly with the colour of your natural brow hairs. Ideal for drawing precise, hair-like strokes or for completely filling in your brows. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy you'll love it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLong-lasting formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e0% synthetic colourants\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologically and ophthalmologically tested\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFragrance allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Brow Pencil features a wooden barrel and recyclable plastic caps while the box is made from sustainably sourced paper.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eComb and shape your eyebrows with the built-in spoolie, following their natural curve. Create a natural brow look by drawing soft, hair-like strokes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e C10-18 TRIGLYCERIDES; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA*; EUPHORBIA CERIFERA CERA; HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*; MICA (CI 77019); CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES); TOCOPHEROL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL; ASCORBYL PALMITATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e16% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52308727857479,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-the-brow-pencil-medium-brown-1g-9283436.jpg?v=1762389183"},{"product_id":"madara-the-brow-pencil-medium-brown-1g-copy","title":"MÁDARA The Brow Pencil Dark Brown 1g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis creamy eyebrow pencil glides onto the skin smoothly, shaping your brows for a defined and polished look. Formulated with mineral pigments, providing long-lasting shades that blend seamlessly with the colour of your natural brow hairs. Ideal for drawing precise, hair-like strokes or for completely filling in your brows. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy you'll love it. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLong-lasting formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e0% synthetic colourants\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologically and ophthalmologically tested\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFragrance allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Brow Pencil features a wooden barrel and recyclable plastic caps while the box is made from sustainably sourced paper.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eComb and shape your eyebrows with the built-in spoolie, following their natural curve. Create a natural brow look by drawing soft, hair-like strokes. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eC10-18 TRIGLYCERIDES; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA*; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); EUPHORBIA CERIFERA CERA; HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*; MICA (CI 77019); CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ; CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES); TOCOPHEROL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL; ASCORBYL PALMITATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e17% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52308730609991,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-the-brow-pencil-dark-brown-1g-3488735.jpg?v=1762389189"},{"product_id":"madara-midsummer-soft-silk-mineral-bronzer-9g","title":"MÁDARA Midsummer Soft Silk Mineral Bronzer #1 Heat 9g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAchieve a naturally sun-kissed appearance with this silky mineral powder bronzer. The talc-free formula, enriched with coated pigments and glistening mineral particles, adapts to your skin's texture for a flawless, seamless blend. The finely milled powder feels almost air-like on the skin, ensuring comfortable wear all day long. Suitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to the hollows of your cheeks for a defined, contoured appearance. For a naturally sun-kissed glow, lightly dust across your cheeks, forehead, nose bridge and chin. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e MICA (CI 77019)**; KAOLIN; CALCIUM CARBONATE; LAUROYL LYSINE; ZINC STEARATE; SILICA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; LECITHIN; CAPRYLYL GLYCOL; TOCOPHEROL; ARGANIA SPINOSA (ARGAN) KERNEL OIL*; GLYCINE SOJA (SOYBEAN) OIL; AROMA; CERA ALBA (BEESWAX)*; GLYCOLIPIDS; AQUA; GLYCERIN; POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIISOSTEARATE; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) EXTRACT; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) GERM EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; LINALOOL***; GERANIOL***; GERANYL ACETATE***; VANILLIN; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) **; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)**\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e***From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52634451018055,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-midsummer-soft-silk-mineral-bronzer-1-heat-9g-3239946.jpg?v=1762389187"},{"product_id":"madara-moonlight-soft-glow-mineral-highlighter-1-stardust","title":"MÁDARA Moonlight Soft Glow Mineral Highlighter, #1 Stardust 6g","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile nothing beats the magical glow of moonlit skin, this natural highlighter comes delightfully close. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eInfused with ultra-refined, light-reflecting mineral particles, it delivers a soft, iridescent finish that looks just like your skin — only more luminous. The talc-free formula with skin-loving ingredients blends effortlessly, adapting to your skin’s texture. Suitable for fair to medium skin. \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eSweep onto the high points of your face — cheekbones, brow bones, bridge of the nose and cupid’s bow — using a brush or fingertips. Blend gently for a soft glow or layer for a more intense radiance. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e MICA (CI 77019)**; LAUROYL LYSINE; ZINC STEARATE; SILICA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; LECITHIN; CAPRYLYL GLYCOL; TOCOPHEROL; ARGANIA SPINOSA (ARGAN) KERNEL OIL*; GLYCINE SOJA (SOYBEAN) OIL*; AROMA; CERA ALBA (BEESWAX)*; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; AQUA; GLYCERIN; POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIISOSTEARATE; GLYCOLIPIDS; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) EXTRACT; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) GERM EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; LINALOOL***; GERANIOL***; GERANYL ACETATE***; VANILLIN; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) **; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)**\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e***From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52634465141063,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-moonlight-soft-glow-mineral-highlighter-1-stardust-6g-4312432.jpg?v=1762389188"},{"product_id":"madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-501-flattery-3-8g","title":"MÁDARA Dazzle Nights Satin Shine Lipstick, #501 Flattery 3,8g","description":"\u003cp\u003eDrench your lips in dreamy, pigment-loaded colour and subtle lustre that pay homage to the glistening textures and bold hues of the 80s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe opulent, vegan formula made with nourishing oils, shea butter and vitamins C+E  goes on smooth, wearing off gradually and delicately while hydrating lips from the inside out. \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFormulated with pure mineral pigments, leaving out synthetic or animal-derived colourants. Dermatologically tested.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply directly to clean, moisturised lips. For an extra glossy finish, layer MÁDARA Glossy Venom Hydrating Lip Gloss on top.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e OCTYLDODECANOL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL; POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE; SORBITAN OLIVATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; CAPRYLOYL GLYCERIN\/SEBACIC ACID COPOLYMER; CELLULOSE; DILINOLEIC ACID\/PROPANEDIOL COPOLYMER; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; MICA (CI 77019)***; AROMA; DIPALMITOYL HYDROXYPROLINE; TOCOPHEROL; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; IRVINGIA GABONENSIS KERNEL BUTTER; HYDROGENATED COCO-GLYCERIDES; ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; VACCINIUM MYRTILLUS (BLUEBERRY) SEED OIL*; GLYCOLIPIDS; STEVIA REBAUDIANA EXTRACT; LIMONENE**; TIN OXIDE (CI 77681)***; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)***; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ***; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e8% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52635897266503,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-501-flattery-38g-7415719.jpg?v=1762389193"},{"product_id":"madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-503-charisma-3-8g","title":"MÁDARA Dazzle Nights Satin Shine Lipstick, #503 Charisma 3.8g","description":"\u003cp\u003eDrench your lips in dreamy, pigment-loaded colour and subtle lustre that pay homage to the glistening textures and bold hues of the 80s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe opulent, vegan formula made with nourishing oils, shea butter and vitamins C+E  goes on smooth, wearing off gradually and delicately while hydrating lips from the inside out. \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFormulated with pure mineral pigments, leaving out synthetic or animal-derived colourants. Dermatologically tested.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply directly to clean, moisturised lips. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e OCTYLDODECANOL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL; POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE; SORBITAN OLIVATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; CAPRYLOYL GLYCERIN\/SEBACIC ACID COPOLYMER; CELLULOSE; DILINOLEIC ACID\/PROPANEDIOL COPOLYMER; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; AROMA; DIPALMITOYL HYDROXYPROLINE; TOCOPHEROL; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; MICA (CI 77019)***; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; IRVINGIA GABONENSIS KERNEL BUTTER; HYDROGENATED COCO-GLYCERIDES; ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; VACCINIUM MYRTILLUS (BLUEBERRY) SEED OIL*; GLYCOLIPIDS; STEVIA REBAUDIANA EXTRACT; LIMONENE**; TIN OXIDE (CI 77681)***; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)***; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ***; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)***; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e10% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636034400583,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-503-charisma-38g-4689050.jpg?v=1762389190"},{"product_id":"madara-velvet-wear-matte-cream-lipstick-33-magma","title":"MÁDARA Velvet Wear Matte Cream Lipstick, #33 Magma","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis velvety, ultra-spreadable lipstick glides onto the lips easily and effortlessly, ensuring a beautiful colour payoff, comfortable wear and soft satin finish. The antioxidant-bursting formula with blueberry seed oil and shea butter nurtures and protects the skin, ensuring smooth and silky lips. This lipstick is formulated with pure mineral pigments, leaving out synthetic and animal-derived colourants.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse elaborately for a classic matte lip look. Apply carelessly and dab it in with fingers to achieve the trendy lip stain effect. Top with your favourite lip gloss for extra shine and dimension.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can also apply it onto your eyelids and cheeks for a monochrome makeup look.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL; COCO-CAPRYLATE; DICAPRYLYL CARBONATE; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; CAPRYLOYL GLYCERIN\/SEBACIC ACID COPOLYMER; CELLULOSE; POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE; SILICA; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; TOCOPHEROL; AROMA; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE; GLYCOLIPIDS; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; VACCINIUM MYRTILLUS (BLUEBERRY) SEED OIL*; BETAINE; STEVIA REBAUDIANA EXTRACT; TRICALCIUM PHOSPHATE; VANILLIN; CITRUS AURANTIUM PEEL OIL; LIMONENE**; MICA (CI 77019); CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ; TIN OXIDE; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636068479303,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-velvet-wear-matte-cream-lipstick-33-magma-4529450.jpg?v=1762389124"},{"product_id":"madara-deep-matter-bold-volume-mascara-6ml","title":"MÁDARA Deep Matter Bold Volume Mascara, 6ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eIntensify your gaze with this buildable, high-performance mascara featuring all-natural pigments for a jet black finish. Packed with nourishing actives, it reinforces your lashes while creating phenomenal volume, definition and length. The high-definition wand reaches even the tiniest of lashes, while the formula uses natural vegan waxes and plant-derived peptides for easy application and incredible lasting power. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply one coat for a classic, natural look, or add more coats for extra intensity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e AQUA; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)***; STEARIC ACID; HELIANTHUS ANNUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED CERA; GLYCERIN**; COPERNICIA CERIFERA (CARNAUBA) WAX; OLEA EUROPAEA (OLIVE) OIL UNSAPONIFIABLES; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; CELLULOSE; PENTYLENE GLYCOL; PULLULAN; OCTYLDODECANOL; GLYCERYL STEARATE; PISUM SATIVUM PEPTIDE; POLYGLYCERYL-10 LAURATE; SORBITOL; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; SHOREA ROBUSTA RESIN; GLYCERYL CAPRYLATE\/ CAPRATE; PALMITIC ACID; POTASSIUM HYDROXIDE; ACACIA SENEGAL GUM; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; XANTHAN GUM; TREHALOSE; CITRIC ACID; LEUCONOSTOC\/RADISH ROOT FERMENT FILTRATE; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Made using Organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636125856071,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-deep-matter-bold-volume-mascara-6ml-9410971.png?v=1771049349"},{"product_id":"madara-come-closer-infinite-lash-mascara-6ml","title":"MÁDARA Come Closer Infinite Lash Mascara, 6ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover the outstanding combination of effortless volume and well-defined separation with the Come Closer Infinite Lash Mascara. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe natural certified formula stars vegan waxes to ensure smooth application and lasting performance, while plant-derived peptides and organic castor oil encourage fuller, stronger lashes over time.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFeaturing a unique conical shape, the classic fibre brush coats each lash in jet black, all-natural pigment to give enviable volume, length and definition.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply one coat to clean lashes for a natural look, or use in layers to intensify. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e AQUA; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)***; STEARIC ACID; HELIANTHUS ANNUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED CERA; GLYCERIN**; COPERNICIA CERIFERA (CARNAUBA) WAX; OLEA EUROPAEA (OLIVE) OIL UNSAPONIFIABLES; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; CELLULOSE; PENTYLENE GLYCOL; PULLULAN; OCTYLDODECANOL; GLYCERYL STEARATE; PISUM SATIVUM PEPTIDE; POLYGLYCERYL-10 LAURATE; SORBITOL; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; SHOREA ROBUSTA RESIN; GLYCERYL CAPRYLATE\/ CAPRATE; PALMITIC ACID; POTASSIUM HYDROXIDE; ACACIA SENEGAL GUM; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; XANTHAN GUM; TREHALOSE; CITRIC ACID; LEUCONOSTOC\/RADISH ROOT FERMENT FILTRATE; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL*\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Made using Organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636200206663,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-come-closer-infinite-lash-mascara-6ml-7855214.jpg?v=1762389187"},{"product_id":"madara-grow-fix-brow-lash-booster-4-25ml","title":"MÁDARA Grow \u0026 Fix Brow \u0026 Lash Booster, 4,25ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis double-action serum recharges your brows and lashes with length, shine and volume to create a fuller and healthier look.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eShapes and fixes your brows for any desired look.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse on brows and lashes to boost hair growth, fix and add shine. Apply on bare lashes or brows, or use it as the finishing touch on your brows to fix the hairs in place. Shake before use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e AQUA; CANTHARELLUS CIBARIUS (CHANTERELLE) EXTRACT*; PULLULAN; GLYCERIN**; PISUM SATIVUM PEPTIDE; SORBITOL; URTICA DIOICA (NETTLE) LEAF EXTRACT*; ZINC PCA; SCLEROTIUM GUM; CAFFEINE; SODIUM LEVULINATE; ACACIA SENEGAL GUM; SODIUM BENZOATE; POTASSIUM HYDROXIDE; HEXAPEPTIDE-11; TREHALOSE; LEUCONOSTOC\/RADISH ROOT FERMENT FILTRATE; SODIUM PHYTATE; AROMA; POTASSIUM SORBATE; SODIUM HYALURONATE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636262433095,"sku":null,"price":26.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-grow-fix-brow-lash-booster-425ml-4935191.jpg?v=1762389121"},{"product_id":"madara-air-equal-soft-silk-mineral-powder-2-beige","title":"MÁDARA Air Equal Soft Silk Mineral Powder, #2 Beige, 9g","description":"\u003cp\u003eMade by tinted makeup experts, this weightless mineral powder is created to care for your skin as it banishes shine, diffuses the look of pores and smooths fine lines.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eLike a soft-focus filter for your complexion, the ultra-fine formula glides onto skin effortlessly, setting makeup for extended wear and giving an invisible, airbrushed finish.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eEnriched with natural retouching particles, white clay and vitamin E, to grant a comfortable all-day wear while protecting the skin from external stressors.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eDermatologically tested. Free from titanium dioxide and talc.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply powder all over the face with a brush or puff to set makeup.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e MICA (CI 77019)***; CALCIUM CARBONATE; KAOLIN; LAUROYL LYSINE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) STARCH; ZINC STEARATE; SILICA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; ARGANIA SPINOSA (ARGAN) KERNEL OIL*; CAPRYLYL GLYCOL; CELLULOSE; TOCOPHEROL; GLYCINE SOJA (SOYBEAN) OIL*; AROMA; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; GLYCOLIPIDS; AQUA; GLYCERIN; POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIISOSTEARATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) EXTRACT; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) GERM EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; LINALOOL**; GERANIOL**; GERANYL ACETATE**; VANILLIN; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636326134087,"sku":null,"price":28.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-air-equal-soft-silk-mineral-powder-2-beige-9g-9913215.jpg?v=1762389191"},{"product_id":"madara-air-equal-soft-silk-mineral-powder-2-fair-9g","title":"MÁDARA Air Equal Soft Silk Mineral Powder, #2 Fair, 9g","description":"\u003cp\u003eMade by tinted makeup experts, this weightless mineral powder is created to care for your skin as it banishes shine, diffuses the look of pores and smooths fine lines.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eLike a soft-focus filter for your complexion, the ultra-fine formula glides onto skin effortlessly, setting makeup for extended wear and giving an invisible, airbrushed finish.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eEnriched with natural retouching particles, white clay and vitamin E, to grant a comfortable all-day wear while protecting the skin from external stressors.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eDermatologically tested. Free from titanium dioxide and talc.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply powder all over the face with a brush or puff to set makeup.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e MICA (CI 77019)***; CALCIUM CARBONATE; KAOLIN; LAUROYL LYSINE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) STARCH; ZINC STEARATE; SILICA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; ARGANIA SPINOSA (ARGAN) KERNEL OIL*; CAPRYLYL GLYCOL; CELLULOSE; TOCOPHEROL; GLYCINE SOJA (SOYBEAN) OIL*; AROMA; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; GLYCOLIPIDS; AQUA; GLYCERIN; POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIISOSTEARATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) EXTRACT; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) GERM EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; LINALOOL**; GERANIOL**; GERANYL ACETATE**; VANILLIN; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636406710599,"sku":null,"price":28.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-air-equal-soft-silk-mineral-powder-2-fair-9g-2409786.jpg?v=1762389185"},{"product_id":"madara-magnetic-blush-mineral-cheek-blusher-1-fierce-flame","title":"MÁDARA Magnetic Blush Mineral Cheek Blusher, #1 Fierce Flame, 6g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFrom vibrant red beet juice to subtle high-tech powder formulas, blush has remained a timeless classic throughout the decades and trends. This satin matte blush blends seamlessly with your complexion for a natural, skin-like flush that barely looks made up. The talc-free formula features glycolipid-coated mineral pigments that adapt to your skin's unique texture, delivering a flawlessly smooth finish for the most natural-looking blush. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eDiffuse a small amount on the cheeks, nose and eyelids for a naturally flushed look. Layer on the cheeks for a lifted appearance. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e MICA (CI 77019)**; CALCIUM CARBONATE; KAOLIN; LAUROYL LYSINE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) STARCH; ZINC STEARATE; SILICA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; ARGANIA SPINOSA (ARGAN) KERNEL OIL*; CAPRYLYL GLYCOL; CELLULOSE; TOCOPHEROL; GLYCINE SOJA (SOYBEAN) OIL; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; AQUA; GLYCERIN; GLYCOLIPIDS; POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIISOSTEARATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) EXTRACT; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) GERM EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; AROMA; LINALOOL***; GERANIOL***; GERANYL ACETATE***; VANILLIN; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)**\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e***From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636472672583,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-magnetic-blush-mineral-cheek-blusher-1-fierce-flame-6g-7944376.jpg?v=1762389128"},{"product_id":"madara-magnetic-blush-mineral-cheek-blusher-1-fierce-flame-copy","title":"MÁDARA Magnetic Blush Mineral Cheek Blusher, #2 Bare Blossom, 6g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFrom vibrant red beet juice to subtle high-tech powder formulas, blush has remained a timeless classic throughout the decades and trends. This satin matte blush blends seamlessly with your complexion for a natural, skin-like flush that barely looks made up. The talc-free formula features glycolipid-coated mineral pigments that adapt to your skin's unique texture, delivering a flawlessly smooth finish for the most natural-looking blush. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eDiffuse a small amount on the cheeks, nose and eyelids for a naturally flushed look. Layer on the cheeks for a lifted appearance. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e MICA (CI 77019)**; CALCIUM CARBONATE; KAOLIN; LAUROYL LYSINE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) STARCH; ZINC STEARATE; SILICA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; ARGANIA SPINOSA (ARGAN) KERNEL OIL*; CAPRYLYL GLYCOL; CELLULOSE; TOCOPHEROL; GLYCINE SOJA (SOYBEAN) OIL; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; AQUA; GLYCERIN; GLYCOLIPIDS; POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIISOSTEARATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) EXTRACT; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) GERM EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; AROMA; LINALOOL***; GERANIOL***; GERANYL ACETATE***; VANILLIN; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)**; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)**; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)**\